WEBVTT

01:32.340 --> 01:35.020
[How dare you!?]

01:35.070 --> 01:37.940
[Episode 13]

02:04.200 --> 02:04.730
I'm sorry

02:05.590 --> 02:06.150
I'm late.

02:07.950 --> 02:09.880
If I had gone to see her one last time

02:11.590 --> 02:13.590
and talked things through with her,

02:15.000 --> 02:16.150
Mei wouldn't have...

02:16.150 --> 02:17.810
No one can predict the future.

02:18.310 --> 02:19.860
You didn't do anything wrong.

02:18.710 --> 02:19.710
♪ Tell me ♪

02:20.360 --> 02:23.870
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

02:25.430 --> 02:26.579
♪ Walk past me ♪

02:26.960 --> 02:30.710
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

02:27.310 --> 02:29.079
I'm so useless.

02:31.600 --> 02:34.110
Why am I so useless?

02:31.970 --> 02:34.500
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

02:35.360 --> 02:38.140
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

02:35.880 --> 02:37.110
You're just human.

02:38.870 --> 02:44.620
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

02:43.230 --> 02:44.360
It must hurt, right?

02:45.740 --> 02:46.829
♪ Blame me ♪

02:46.910 --> 02:48.310
Even though she was just a 2D character,

02:47.530 --> 02:50.990
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

02:49.070 --> 02:50.670
you've known her for so long.

02:52.579 --> 02:53.650
♪ Hide me ♪

02:52.750 --> 02:54.310
I know how much she means to you.

02:54.130 --> 02:58.180
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

02:57.840 --> 02:58.440
It's okay.

02:59.579 --> 03:01.940
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

02:59.930 --> 03:00.920
Cry if you want.

03:02.780 --> 03:05.430
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

03:03.030 --> 03:03.560
I'm here.

03:06.280 --> 03:09.240
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

03:09.260 --> 03:11.420
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

03:11.820 --> 03:14.270
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

03:14.320 --> 03:16.079
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

03:16.110 --> 03:18.630
♪ I never yielded ♪

03:18.940 --> 03:20.380
♪ But why ♪

03:20.700 --> 03:25.170
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

03:25.570 --> 03:27.940
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

03:27.980 --> 03:29.829
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

03:28.000 --> 03:28.680
I'm sorry.

03:29.860 --> 03:32.240
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

03:30.630 --> 03:31.760
That day on the lake,

03:32.600 --> 03:34.360
♪ The first time I met you ♪

03:33.160 --> 03:35.150
I shouldn't have suspected you of
staging the whole thing yourself.

03:34.730 --> 03:37.910
♪ There was once light ♪

03:38.470 --> 03:46.829
♪ In my soul ♪

03:38.880 --> 03:39.560
It's okay.

03:42.590 --> 03:43.850
I know you were scared.

03:46.190 --> 03:47.920
I didn't think things through.

03:49.240 --> 03:50.700
Give me a little more time.

03:51.920 --> 03:53.280
I'll try to adapt.

03:52.960 --> 03:55.450
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

03:53.800 --> 03:55.130
You don't have to adapt.

03:55.500 --> 03:57.260
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

03:57.290 --> 03:59.810
♪ I never yielded ♪

03:58.800 --> 04:00.120
From now on, if there's ever
danger like this again,

04:00.120 --> 04:01.640
♪ But why ♪

04:01.280 --> 04:03.000
or anything that requires
getting your hands dirty,

04:01.850 --> 04:06.410
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

04:04.860 --> 04:05.790
let me handle it.

04:06.750 --> 04:09.110
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

04:08.870 --> 04:09.560
Why?

04:09.160 --> 04:11.010
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

04:10.150 --> 04:11.010
Did you forget?

04:11.040 --> 04:13.420
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

04:12.750 --> 04:13.630
I'm an actor.

04:13.780 --> 04:15.570
♪ The first time I met you ♪

04:15.630 --> 04:17.240
I can play any role

04:16.130 --> 04:24.030
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

04:17.240 --> 04:19.040
without psychological burden.

04:23.430 --> 04:23.950
And you—

04:29.560 --> 04:30.960
you never have to change.

04:44.680 --> 04:47.159
Maid Mei's assassination attempt
on Consort Shu was exposed.

04:47.159 --> 04:49.720
Concubine Yu had a fierce quarrel
with His Majesty,

04:49.720 --> 04:52.430
and in a fit of anger, His Majesty
consigned her to the Cold Palace.

04:52.430 --> 04:54.430
But instead of admitting her fault,

04:54.680 --> 04:57.000
Concubine Yu urged His Majesty
to get rid of Consort Shu,

04:57.000 --> 04:58.070
claiming

04:59.920 --> 05:01.650
she had dreamt that Consort Shu

05:02.040 --> 05:04.100
would one day kill her entire family.

05:06.840 --> 05:07.510
Dreamt?

05:08.510 --> 05:10.190
Of course His Majesty didn't believe her.

05:10.190 --> 05:13.430
He rebuked Concubine Yu for making
jealous, baseless claims to gain favor.

05:13.430 --> 05:14.230
Your Majesty.

05:14.720 --> 05:16.870
If Consort Shu's family hadn't
plotted against my father first,

05:16.870 --> 05:18.480
Mei would never have tried to
assassinate her for no reason.

05:18.480 --> 05:19.810
How dare you argue back!

05:19.830 --> 05:21.560
I've been too lenient with you—

05:21.560 --> 05:23.270
that you dare behave so outrageously!

05:23.270 --> 05:25.160
Why won't Your Majesty believe me?

05:25.160 --> 05:25.620
Shut up!

05:26.510 --> 05:28.040
You will stay here
and reflect on your actions.

05:28.040 --> 05:28.840
Your Majesty!

05:29.000 --> 05:30.410
-Nail the doors and windows shut,
-Your Majesty!

05:30.410 --> 05:31.740
[Office of Drums and Bells]

05:30.600 --> 05:32.270
and post guards outside to watch her.

05:32.270 --> 05:33.270
Without my order,

05:33.830 --> 05:35.920
no one is to bring Concubine Yu any food!

05:35.920 --> 05:37.430
Concubine Yu was beside herself with rage,

05:37.430 --> 05:38.960
and what she said afterward

05:39.390 --> 05:41.230
grew more and more incoherent.

05:42.390 --> 05:43.230
Heartless!

05:43.430 --> 05:44.360
Without my abilities,

05:44.360 --> 05:46.020
you, Xiahou Dan, are nothing!

05:47.190 --> 05:48.830
We servants were terrified.

05:49.310 --> 05:50.680
She actually dared to defy His Majesty

05:50.680 --> 05:52.480
and even called him by his personal name.

05:52.480 --> 05:54.310
No one had ever seen such a scene before.

05:54.310 --> 05:55.770
How did His Majesty react?

05:56.159 --> 05:58.360
Naturally, His Majesty flew into a rage

05:59.000 --> 06:01.680
and immediately stripped Concubine Yu
of her title.

06:01.680 --> 06:02.070
I see.

06:03.360 --> 06:04.890
Go and receive your reward.

06:05.630 --> 06:07.090
Thank you, Your Highness.

06:13.430 --> 06:14.160
Gentlemen,

06:15.680 --> 06:17.410
what do you make of this matter?

06:17.750 --> 06:18.610
Your Highness,

06:20.160 --> 06:22.480
Consort Shu's family and the Yu family

06:23.120 --> 06:24.750
had long been at odds.

06:25.870 --> 06:27.160
After Concubine Yu gained favor,

06:27.160 --> 06:29.270
she kept Consort Shu
thoroughly suppressed.

06:29.270 --> 06:31.400
Now that Minister Yu has been demoted,

06:31.560 --> 06:34.360
Consort Shu's family is indeed
plotting in secret

06:34.510 --> 06:36.510
to poison him on his way to exile

06:36.680 --> 06:38.680
and eliminate Minister Yu for good.

06:39.240 --> 06:43.040
Using maid Mei to eliminate Consort Shu

06:43.800 --> 06:47.130
would benefit Concubine Yu
whether it succeeded or failed—

06:48.040 --> 06:50.640
a perfect two-birds-with-one-stone scheme.

06:51.270 --> 06:52.130
Your Highness,

06:52.240 --> 06:53.190
I think

06:53.390 --> 06:55.590
this woman is not to be underestimated.

06:55.630 --> 06:58.120
But there's one thing I don't understand

06:58.870 --> 07:00.800
which feels somewhat suspicious.

07:01.430 --> 07:01.830
Speak.

07:02.640 --> 07:04.640
Consort Shu's family acts in secret

07:05.190 --> 07:06.920
and hasn't yet made their move,

07:07.430 --> 07:09.750
while the Yu family remains
completely unaware.

07:09.750 --> 07:10.920
Even we officials

07:11.480 --> 07:14.080
only uncovered it
after considerable effort.

07:16.230 --> 07:19.030
How could Consort Yu,
secluded deep in the palace,

07:19.490 --> 07:21.630
know about future events?

07:22.240 --> 07:23.440
She couldn't have had

07:24.430 --> 07:25.720
foresight, could she?

07:26.630 --> 07:27.230
Nonsense.

07:32.310 --> 07:34.710
This is getting more and more interesting.

07:36.680 --> 07:38.409
Gentlemen, please have mercy.

07:38.960 --> 07:45.620
[Office of Drums and Bells]

07:39.430 --> 07:41.070
Please give me some food.

07:42.190 --> 07:42.680
Buddy.

07:43.830 --> 07:44.830
Buddy, look at me!

07:46.750 --> 07:48.550
Buddy, please pass a word for me—

07:48.830 --> 07:50.360
tell them Wanyin did nothing wrong.

07:50.360 --> 07:51.890
I really did nothing wrong.

07:56.580 --> 07:58.390
Why is this door even harder than stone?

07:58.390 --> 07:59.320
It hurts so much.

08:20.040 --> 08:20.700
You guys...

08:21.120 --> 08:21.830
Your Highness.

08:21.830 --> 08:22.190
Your Highness.

08:22.190 --> 08:23.050
Your Highness.

08:30.600 --> 08:31.000
Hello.

08:31.950 --> 08:32.880
Why are you here?

08:35.789 --> 08:37.669
I just dug a tunnel,
which is narrow and cramped.

08:37.669 --> 08:39.390
Took me forever to crawl through.

08:39.390 --> 08:40.289
I wanted to ask you,

08:40.289 --> 08:42.090
what would you like to eat later?

08:42.700 --> 08:44.960
What could there be to eat
in the Cold Palace?

08:44.960 --> 08:45.420
Hotpot?

08:46.550 --> 08:48.320
Why are you so obsessed with hotpot?

08:48.320 --> 08:50.320
Aren't you the one who loves hotpot?

08:53.480 --> 08:54.340
Nine-grid pot?

08:55.260 --> 08:56.990
I'd rather have a yin-yang pot.

08:57.320 --> 08:58.000
I knew it.

08:58.590 --> 09:00.630
With some chilled mung bean sweet soup.

09:00.630 --> 09:01.420
All set!

09:04.360 --> 09:07.420
This Cold Palace isn't so bad
once you tidy it up, right?

09:07.880 --> 09:10.210
Maybe we should just move in here
for good.

09:11.870 --> 09:12.990
Nonsense.

09:22.000 --> 09:23.570
This used to be a storage room
for the music bureau.

09:23.570 --> 09:25.370
There's all sorts of stuff here.

09:25.670 --> 09:26.730
But there's no pot.

09:27.120 --> 09:27.650
Says who?

09:33.950 --> 09:35.230
Crawling through that tunnel

09:35.230 --> 09:37.720
with this pot on my back
was truly exhausting.

09:37.720 --> 09:38.650
That's nothing.

09:38.750 --> 09:40.480
I was carrying a table, okay?

09:41.770 --> 09:42.970
You're the real hero.

09:48.590 --> 09:50.360
What's the latest news outside?

09:50.360 --> 09:52.440
The commander of the Imperial Guards
got drunk last night

09:52.440 --> 09:54.100
and drowned in the lotus pond.

09:54.270 --> 09:55.240
It was Prince Duan's doing.

09:55.240 --> 09:56.550
He's following Xu Yao's plan,
gradually eroding

09:56.550 --> 09:58.910
the Empress Dowager's faction's power
step by step.

09:58.910 --> 09:59.510
Just wait—

09:59.720 --> 10:01.850
the court is going to get lively again.

10:04.240 --> 10:05.900
But there's one more problem.

10:07.550 --> 10:09.480
Ever since you confined me to
the Cold Palace,

10:09.480 --> 10:12.390
Prince Duan has been sending letters
frequently, trying to win me over.

10:12.390 --> 10:13.360
He still hasn't given up on

10:13.360 --> 10:15.690
finding out who the expert
by your side is.

10:16.390 --> 10:17.590
Here, Your Highness.

10:17.600 --> 10:18.460
Have some tripe.

10:18.460 --> 10:19.920
It's okay. Help yourself.

10:20.150 --> 10:21.010
That's omasum.

10:21.630 --> 10:22.430
This is tripe.

10:30.320 --> 10:31.450
They taste similar.

10:34.870 --> 10:35.480
Right.

10:38.260 --> 10:39.840
Since they taste similar,

10:42.120 --> 10:43.280
when he wants tripe,

10:43.870 --> 10:45.800
I can just give him omasum instead.

10:47.730 --> 10:48.880
So you mean

10:49.320 --> 10:50.520
a bait and switch?

10:50.540 --> 10:51.920
Exactly—a classic decoy maneuver.

10:51.920 --> 10:53.620
There's a secret guard
by the Empress Dowager's side

10:53.620 --> 10:54.880
with a scar on his face.

10:55.050 --> 10:56.980
And Mr. Bei knows the Disguise Art.

10:57.080 --> 11:00.540
-What a coincidence, isn't it?
-What a coincidence, isn't it?

11:00.670 --> 11:01.380
Are you two

11:01.750 --> 11:02.950
speaking in riddles?

11:03.030 --> 11:04.390
I don't understand a single word.

11:04.390 --> 11:05.390
You're not supposed to.

11:05.390 --> 11:06.230
Just eat.

11:06.870 --> 11:07.330
Come on.

11:09.360 --> 11:10.910
I have a plan.

11:11.630 --> 11:13.320
His Majesty is wary of me...

11:14.000 --> 11:14.800
That's right.

11:14.910 --> 11:15.480
Yet he

11:16.390 --> 11:18.590
dreads anyone else gaining my support,

11:19.120 --> 11:22.250
so he's kept me imprisoned
the Cold Palace all this time.

11:24.840 --> 11:26.840
These hopeless, miserable days...

11:28.030 --> 11:30.440
Are truly unbearable.

11:33.080 --> 11:34.810
Hearing of your mistreatment,

11:35.000 --> 11:36.240
my heart is aflame with worry

11:35.020 --> 11:36.470
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

11:36.490 --> 11:38.160
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

11:36.630 --> 11:38.090
and I'm deeply concerned.

11:38.480 --> 11:39.240
I only hope that you, Wanyin,

11:38.580 --> 11:39.750
♪ Incredible ♪

11:39.690 --> 11:40.870
will keep yourself safe,

11:40.200 --> 11:41.300
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

11:41.550 --> 11:42.670
so that you can have a chance
to plan for the future.

11:41.850 --> 11:42.790
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

11:42.960 --> 11:44.560
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

11:44.930 --> 11:46.090
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

11:45.030 --> 11:45.890
Your Highness,

11:46.150 --> 11:47.620
if you truly care for me,

11:46.530 --> 11:47.900
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

11:48.170 --> 11:50.950
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

11:48.630 --> 11:50.690
I'll certainly do my best to help you.

11:51.290 --> 11:52.880
♪ From day to night ♪

11:52.360 --> 11:54.750
But royal favor is so fleeting.

11:53.020 --> 11:54.450
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

11:54.540 --> 11:56.060
♪ From the present to the past ♪

11:56.210 --> 11:57.340
♪ It's always you ♪

11:56.360 --> 11:57.830
Your Highness, how are you different

11:57.830 --> 11:59.330
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

11:58.600 --> 11:59.840
from His Majesty?

11:59.350 --> 12:00.930
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

12:00.950 --> 12:03.840
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

12:04.160 --> 12:07.260
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

12:07.320 --> 12:09.220
♪ With you ♪

12:09.730 --> 12:12.040
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

12:11.440 --> 12:12.440
It looks really like you.

12:12.090 --> 12:13.650
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

12:13.220 --> 12:13.850
[If Your Highness truly cares for me,
I'll certainly do my best to help you.]

12:13.720 --> 12:15.670
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

12:13.880 --> 12:14.640
[But royal favor is so fleeting.
Your Highness, how are you different]

12:14.670 --> 12:15.190
[from His Majesty?]

12:15.610 --> 12:16.690
There are many differences, of course.

12:16.170 --> 12:18.520
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

12:18.150 --> 12:19.270
I only wish that one day,

12:18.570 --> 12:20.080
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

12:19.720 --> 12:21.390
I could enjoy the Lantern Festival lights

12:20.100 --> 12:22.120
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

12:22.000 --> 12:24.390
amid the splendor of fireworks
with you, Wanyin.

12:24.390 --> 12:26.590
The sooner you help me succeed, Wanyin,

12:26.750 --> 12:29.150
the sooner I can rescue you
from this peril.

12:32.590 --> 12:34.020
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

12:34.180 --> 12:35.840
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

12:34.270 --> 12:35.080
I'm so hungry.

12:37.270 --> 12:39.080
Please give me more food.

12:40.240 --> 12:41.630
I'm starving.

12:48.990 --> 12:50.210
♪ Incredible ♪

12:50.590 --> 12:51.770
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

12:52.190 --> 12:53.220
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

12:53.300 --> 12:54.950
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

12:55.290 --> 12:56.490
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

12:56.960 --> 12:58.190
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

12:58.540 --> 13:01.400
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

13:01.150 --> 13:02.440
Pie in the sky?

13:01.650 --> 13:03.320
♪ From day to night ♪

13:03.400 --> 13:04.930
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

13:04.990 --> 13:06.540
♪ From the present to the past ♪

13:05.790 --> 13:06.520
In that case,

13:06.610 --> 13:07.720
♪ It's always you ♪

13:07.200 --> 13:08.440
I'm willing to help with all my strength.

13:08.270 --> 13:09.700
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

13:09.280 --> 13:11.770
I've already identified the expert
by His Majesty's side

13:09.770 --> 13:11.290
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

13:11.320 --> 13:14.260
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

13:12.390 --> 13:14.120
that Your Highness mentioned.

13:14.630 --> 13:17.670
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

13:17.760 --> 13:19.750
♪ With you ♪

13:20.150 --> 13:22.540
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

13:22.630 --> 13:24.130
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

13:24.200 --> 13:26.100
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

13:26.550 --> 13:28.900
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

13:28.930 --> 13:30.560
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

13:30.580 --> 13:32.510
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

13:42.930 --> 13:44.520
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

13:44.560 --> 13:46.170
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

13:45.480 --> 13:46.400
You blocked it just now.

13:46.400 --> 13:47.910
♪ The wind is blowing gently ♪

13:46.960 --> 13:47.930
You shouldn't have blocked that last move.

13:47.930 --> 13:49.210
♪ Bringing news ♪

13:48.520 --> 13:49.120
Did I?

13:49.390 --> 13:50.880
♪ About your whereabouts ♪

13:49.550 --> 13:50.290
Yes, you did.

13:50.790 --> 13:52.480
You must know all the moves by heart.

13:50.950 --> 13:52.560
♪ Guiding me far away ♪

13:52.930 --> 13:54.100
♪ I carefully ♪

13:53.120 --> 13:53.790
Instinct.

13:54.030 --> 13:54.510
It was out of instinct.

13:54.280 --> 13:55.880
♪ Collect time ♪

13:55.030 --> 13:56.080
I'm just too good.

13:56.040 --> 13:57.860
♪ I'll hide it well ♪

13:56.510 --> 13:57.770
It's lonely at the top.

13:58.080 --> 14:00.560
♪ The secret of meeting you ♪

13:58.590 --> 14:00.790
How about I come up
and keep you company?

14:03.200 --> 14:05.550
Why hasn't Her Highness
finished cutting the melon yet?

14:05.550 --> 14:06.810
I'll go eat some melon.

14:07.670 --> 14:08.960
I've just warmed up.

14:08.570 --> 14:10.080
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

14:10.140 --> 14:11.850
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

14:10.920 --> 14:11.430
Dan.

14:13.630 --> 14:14.890
Come practice with me.

14:33.510 --> 14:34.370
Your Highness.

14:37.030 --> 14:37.960
Have some melon.

14:41.720 --> 14:43.320
Why did you stop practicing?

14:44.080 --> 14:44.960
Just those few moves—

14:44.960 --> 14:45.840
I've mastered them long ago.

14:45.840 --> 14:47.240
You've both worked hard.

14:48.000 --> 14:49.130
We just give orders,

14:49.270 --> 14:50.960
and you run yourselves ragged.

14:50.960 --> 14:51.760
It's nothing—

14:52.150 --> 14:53.410
not worth mentioning.

14:58.840 --> 15:00.500
After this matter is settled,

15:00.960 --> 15:02.020
I'll have to leave.

15:03.440 --> 15:04.080
So soon?

15:05.510 --> 15:08.270
Weren't you ordered by your master
to protect His Majesty?

15:08.270 --> 15:09.960
But with Prince Duan watching,

15:09.960 --> 15:11.960
I can't appear by your side anymore.

15:12.960 --> 15:13.690
That's true.

15:15.720 --> 15:17.980
So, have you decided where you want to go?

15:18.440 --> 15:20.570
His Majesty has given me another task.

15:20.790 --> 15:21.440
What task?

15:23.510 --> 15:24.370
I can't say yet.

15:24.480 --> 15:26.280
You'll know when the time comes.

15:26.750 --> 15:28.350
So there's a secret mission?

15:33.750 --> 15:34.610
Your Highness.

15:39.120 --> 15:40.850
Would you like to leave with me?

15:41.120 --> 15:41.600
What?

15:44.330 --> 15:45.960
From the first time I saw you,

15:46.750 --> 15:48.960
I knew you were a skylark
meant for the open sky,

15:48.960 --> 15:51.090
not to be trapped within palace walls.

15:52.120 --> 15:53.320
As long as you say yes,

15:53.750 --> 15:54.680
I'll take care of

15:54.750 --> 15:56.030
persuading His Majesty.

15:56.030 --> 15:57.320
What are you talking about?

15:57.320 --> 15:59.360
Trying to steal me
right under His Majesty's nose?

15:59.360 --> 16:00.090
I'm serious.

16:00.630 --> 16:01.430
I have a reason

16:01.920 --> 16:03.120
he'll have to accept.

16:03.630 --> 16:04.120
Stop it.

16:04.510 --> 16:05.230
Anyway,

16:05.390 --> 16:07.050
thank you for telling me this.

16:07.840 --> 16:10.370
You don't have to give me an answer
right away.

16:10.510 --> 16:11.200
Please.

16:13.270 --> 16:13.790
Bai,

16:14.670 --> 16:16.070
a fine young hero like you

16:16.270 --> 16:19.130
will surely have a beauty by your side
in the future.

16:23.550 --> 16:24.010
Then...

16:25.600 --> 16:26.910
If it weren't with me,

16:28.090 --> 16:30.350
would you want to go out
and see the world?

16:31.820 --> 16:32.680
Your Highness.

16:34.230 --> 16:35.290
What I want to say is

16:36.070 --> 16:37.530
that beyond this capital,

16:38.060 --> 16:39.660
there's a whole other world.

16:39.870 --> 16:41.440
Once you step beyond these palace walls,

16:41.440 --> 16:42.110
you can

16:42.510 --> 16:44.970
gallop freely on horseback, unrestrained.

16:45.870 --> 16:46.960
Wouldn't a life like that

16:46.960 --> 16:47.960
be exhilarating?

16:51.440 --> 16:52.300
Your Highness.

16:54.000 --> 16:55.530
Think it over for yourself.

16:58.510 --> 17:00.440
Since you've come into this world,

17:01.090 --> 17:02.750
what is it that you truly want?

17:18.750 --> 17:20.400
-In my dream, I saw that
-"In my dream, I saw that

17:20.400 --> 17:22.200
-on the eighth day of October,
-on the eighth day of October,

17:22.200 --> 17:24.750
-the expert rode alone to Zhangtai,
-the expert rode alone to Zhangtai..."

17:24.750 --> 17:26.410
to that entertainment house.

17:27.030 --> 17:28.960
In front of him was a high platform,

17:29.000 --> 17:30.530
behind him a crescent moon,

17:30.920 --> 17:33.580
and it looked like
he was watching a variety act.

17:35.150 --> 17:37.270
The eighth day of October is tomorrow.

17:37.270 --> 17:39.530
Do you believe her words, Your Highness?

17:41.840 --> 17:43.370
Not completely, of course.

17:44.590 --> 17:45.240
So...

17:54.590 --> 17:55.920
Make the arrangements—

17:56.640 --> 17:58.770
I'll pay a visit to the palace tonight.

17:59.430 --> 17:59.850
Yes.

18:22.790 --> 18:23.320
Yong'er.

18:24.160 --> 18:25.690
Greetings, Your Highness.

18:27.110 --> 18:28.550
You've just recovered from
a serious illness

18:28.550 --> 18:30.480
and recently experienced a shock.

18:31.200 --> 18:33.030
No need for formalities between us.

18:33.030 --> 18:34.920
Thank you for your concern, Your Highness.

18:34.920 --> 18:35.880
I'm fine now.

18:38.270 --> 18:42.310
Zhao Wucheng has successfully taken over
as commander of the Imperial Guards.

18:42.310 --> 18:45.370
I must thank you
for your excellent strategy, Yong'er.

18:46.270 --> 18:48.830
However, there's another
troublesome matter now.

18:48.830 --> 18:51.690
A skilled expert has appeared
by the Emperor's side

18:52.000 --> 18:54.130
and has put me in danger several times.

18:55.200 --> 18:56.860
Yong'er, do you know anything

18:56.960 --> 18:58.020
about this matter?

18:59.030 --> 19:02.000
Is he referring to Bei Zhou,
the supreme martial artist

19:02.000 --> 19:05.000
who has deep connections with the Emperor
in the book?

19:06.110 --> 19:08.920
But I remember
he should appear much later.

19:11.030 --> 19:13.110
I vaguely recall seeing
glimpses of him in my dreams.

19:13.110 --> 19:14.840
This person does seem to exist.

19:19.550 --> 19:20.610
So, Your Highness,

19:21.310 --> 19:23.110
is this why you've come to see me?

19:30.830 --> 19:32.560
Are you angry with me, Yong'er?

19:35.400 --> 19:37.030
As a mere palace consort,

19:38.720 --> 19:41.520
what right do I have to be angry with
Your Highness?

19:42.400 --> 19:44.400
I'm merely lamenting my own fate.

19:46.510 --> 19:48.960
Your Highness, look at the flowers
in this flower house.

19:48.960 --> 19:50.220
Beautiful as they are,

19:50.920 --> 19:53.050
they're confined to this small space.

19:53.310 --> 19:54.070
Tell me,

19:55.350 --> 19:57.750
besides waiting for others to admire them,

19:59.790 --> 20:00.990
what else can they do?

20:09.110 --> 20:09.640
Yong'er.

20:10.590 --> 20:11.990
Perhaps in others' eyes,

20:12.790 --> 20:14.590
I'm a prince close to the people,

20:16.480 --> 20:17.790
a valiant general,

20:19.160 --> 20:21.420
someone expected to become a wise ruler.

20:22.200 --> 20:23.930
But no one actually cares about

20:26.240 --> 20:28.070
what kind of person I truly am

20:32.070 --> 20:33.550
deep down.

20:41.680 --> 20:43.210
Within these palace walls,

20:46.200 --> 20:48.310
I endured the darkest days of my life—

20:51.200 --> 20:52.200
trampled,

20:53.830 --> 20:54.680
humiliated,

20:56.720 --> 20:58.110
whipped—

21:01.440 --> 21:04.030
simply because my mother

21:07.750 --> 21:09.590
was a lowlife in this palace.

21:12.400 --> 21:14.070
I guess she was favored once,

21:15.880 --> 21:17.110
but before long,

21:18.540 --> 21:21.400
she was trampled by
someone even more favored

21:25.440 --> 21:28.570
and became a wronged soul
lingering in this dark palace.

21:33.000 --> 21:35.060
So no one understands better than I do

21:37.350 --> 21:38.550
what this vast palace

21:40.280 --> 21:42.030
means for a woman.

21:45.350 --> 21:47.350
And no one is more desperate than I am

21:47.750 --> 21:51.010
to take her out of this sea of suffering
as soon as possible,

21:52.920 --> 21:55.180
to be together for all lifetimes to come.

21:57.480 --> 21:59.680
But I don't have that ability right now.

22:01.110 --> 22:03.440
Perhaps I shouldn't have approached you,

22:04.640 --> 22:06.700
perhaps I'm not the right man for you,

22:09.310 --> 22:11.510
or perhaps from the very beginning,
I never should have...

22:11.510 --> 22:12.970
Your Highness, I'm sorry.

22:17.270 --> 22:18.600
I was being willful.

22:20.750 --> 22:22.750
I know Your Highness bears the world

22:25.150 --> 22:26.290
on your shoulders.

22:26.960 --> 22:29.960
What is a little grievance on my part
compared to that?

23:16.350 --> 23:17.000
Mr. Bei.

23:17.400 --> 23:18.510
The dagger's finished?

23:18.510 --> 23:20.110
It wasn't difficult to make.

23:20.240 --> 23:21.970
The credit goes to your design.

23:23.350 --> 23:23.680
Look.

23:30.160 --> 23:30.890
Impressive.

23:32.830 --> 23:34.680
As soon as tonight's operation is over,

23:34.680 --> 23:35.830
I'll help Bai leave.

23:36.640 --> 23:37.510
In such a hurry?

23:38.110 --> 23:40.110
Dan's arrangements won't be wrong.

23:43.310 --> 23:45.240
Then I'll go say goodbye to him now.

23:54.240 --> 23:56.300
Last night when I observed the stars,

23:56.750 --> 23:58.010
I noticed those 5 stars

23:58.030 --> 23:59.160
were about to align.

23:59.880 --> 24:00.340
So?

24:03.240 --> 24:05.700
Master's divinations are always accurate,

24:05.750 --> 24:08.150
and he asked me to pass along
one more thing:

24:11.820 --> 24:13.400
your meeting with each other

24:13.400 --> 24:15.320
may not be a blessing after all.

24:18.480 --> 24:19.830
You're just making this up, aren't you?

24:19.830 --> 24:22.230
I wouldn't dare joke about Master's words.

24:24.590 --> 24:25.790
Let her leave sooner—

24:25.880 --> 24:27.410
maybe you both can survive.

24:28.110 --> 24:29.910
If you covet Wanyin, just say so.

24:30.110 --> 24:31.160
I mean well.

24:33.370 --> 24:35.370
Even if you won't think of yourself,

24:35.880 --> 24:37.080
at least think of her.

24:39.030 --> 24:40.810
What does it matter
that you're the Emperor?

24:40.810 --> 24:41.870
Can you protect her

24:42.200 --> 24:43.530
from being mistreated?

24:44.590 --> 24:45.320
That I can do.

24:50.240 --> 24:51.370
Then can you promise

24:51.590 --> 24:53.270
to love only her—to take
just this one ladle from the vast waters?

24:53.270 --> 24:54.270
That's also easy.

24:57.480 --> 24:58.010
Alright.

25:02.070 --> 25:02.510
Fine.

25:03.680 --> 25:05.540
Even if you can do all that you say,

25:05.790 --> 25:07.110
she'll still be a bird in a cage,

25:07.110 --> 25:09.480
never able to roam freely and happily
in this world.

25:09.480 --> 25:09.960
Bai.

25:12.920 --> 25:15.180
The world isn't just for roaming freely.

25:16.110 --> 25:17.570
She has her own ambitions.

25:21.310 --> 25:23.040
You only see her as a little bird

25:23.510 --> 25:24.910
that needs to be set free,

25:25.550 --> 25:26.550
but you fail to see

25:28.200 --> 25:29.800
how upright and noble she is—

25:30.720 --> 25:31.780
radiant as the sun,

25:33.750 --> 25:35.610
able to light up the vast blue sky.

25:41.030 --> 25:41.890
Your Highness.

25:42.830 --> 25:44.360
Think it over for yourself.

25:45.330 --> 25:47.260
Since you've come into this world,

25:47.310 --> 25:48.790
what is it that you truly want?

25:48.790 --> 25:51.160
That kind of life would be wonderful,
of course.

25:51.160 --> 25:53.290
But I have more important things to do.

25:53.950 --> 25:55.010
Bai, you know what?

25:55.480 --> 25:56.640
Back in my hometown,

25:57.420 --> 25:58.920
we liked to use the term
"corporate slaves"

25:58.920 --> 26:00.250
to describe ourselves,

26:01.510 --> 26:02.270
as if

26:03.160 --> 26:04.680
we were all just slaves—

26:05.240 --> 26:07.170
blindfolded and driven by others,

26:07.960 --> 26:10.220
doing meaningless things day after day.

26:11.490 --> 26:12.750
But now I have a chance.

26:13.400 --> 26:15.460
When I'm able to do more for this world

26:15.550 --> 26:17.240
and for more people,

26:19.200 --> 26:21.930
I no longer want to live
just for my own happiness.

26:23.510 --> 26:25.540
The Polaris restores the light in the sky.

26:25.540 --> 26:27.470
A dark omen of royal blood and ruin;

26:27.830 --> 26:29.960
fortune and calamity hang by a thread.

26:30.350 --> 26:31.480
Five stars align,

26:30.630 --> 26:34.350
[The Nameless,
a master beyond the worldly realm]

26:32.790 --> 26:34.920
amidst despair, great fortune rises.

26:40.000 --> 26:43.330
These two people are entangled
in many karmic connections.

26:44.000 --> 26:45.080
Their past lives

26:48.750 --> 26:50.840
are not in this mortal realm.

26:54.200 --> 26:54.930
So annoying.

26:56.310 --> 26:57.570
I'll go pack my things.

26:57.720 --> 26:59.320
But you're right, actually.

27:00.240 --> 27:01.500
It's truly hard for her

27:02.960 --> 27:04.030
to feel happy here.

27:07.170 --> 27:09.230
If one day she fulfills her ambitions

27:09.520 --> 27:10.650
and wishes to leave,

27:13.640 --> 27:15.440
and I'm no longer around by then,

27:17.430 --> 27:18.690
take her away with you.

27:26.550 --> 27:27.810
Don't say such things.

27:29.240 --> 27:30.640
Please, I'm begging you.

27:55.880 --> 27:58.140
Here, Mr. Li. There are still seats here.

27:58.340 --> 27:59.470
Let's go take a look.

27:59.880 --> 28:01.720
This way, sir.

28:03.030 --> 28:05.310
Gentlemen, thank you for
honoring us today

28:05.310 --> 28:06.590
with your generous tips.

28:06.590 --> 28:08.350
I guarantee you'll be satisfied with

28:08.350 --> 28:09.830
our variety acts today.

28:10.200 --> 28:11.240
Fill the wine,

28:11.790 --> 28:12.680
pour the tea,

28:13.550 --> 28:15.070
and let the music begin!

28:15.640 --> 28:16.700
Alright, alright.

28:18.440 --> 28:20.640
Why are you standing here?
Please go upstairs.

28:20.640 --> 28:21.030
Come on.

28:21.030 --> 28:21.560
Alright.

28:25.830 --> 28:26.310
Sir.

28:27.590 --> 28:28.990
What took you so long?

28:29.110 --> 28:30.640
We've been waiting for you.

28:30.970 --> 28:32.700
Come on, have a seat over there.

28:33.900 --> 28:35.320
No rush,

28:35.590 --> 28:36.350
no rush.

28:37.680 --> 28:40.060
Today, we have a newly composed song

28:40.440 --> 28:41.510
called "The Fish Basket Melody."

28:41.510 --> 28:43.240
The new girls are sweet-tongued as honey—

28:43.240 --> 28:45.500
miss them now and you'll regret it later.

28:48.480 --> 28:50.540
Please, come in—upstairs, this way.

29:00.240 --> 29:01.500
My Lord, they're here.

29:02.240 --> 29:03.370
Proceed as planned.

29:03.590 --> 29:03.920
Yes.

29:08.720 --> 29:10.380
Trust me, you won't regret it.

29:12.680 --> 29:14.440
Young master, please drink more.

29:14.440 --> 29:14.970
Alright.

29:21.720 --> 29:23.480
Sir, do you need anything?

29:28.160 --> 29:28.620
Hey,

29:29.000 --> 29:30.830
let's talk things through.

29:32.310 --> 29:33.900
Send our people up

29:34.400 --> 29:36.200
to perform the next variety act.

29:36.310 --> 29:38.640
Don't alarm the audience below the stage.

29:41.920 --> 29:44.080
Sir, drink less next time, alright?

29:57.270 --> 29:57.640
Bravo!

29:57.640 --> 29:58.200
Bravo!

30:00.440 --> 30:01.050
How nice!

30:10.030 --> 30:11.310
Bravo!

30:11.640 --> 30:13.240
Bravo!

30:13.550 --> 30:14.070
Bravo!

30:14.400 --> 30:15.000
Bravo!

30:15.640 --> 30:16.160
They're really skilled.

30:16.160 --> 30:17.400
Yes, truly impressive.

30:17.400 --> 30:18.070
Bravo!

30:18.070 --> 30:19.470
This is truly wonderful.

30:19.960 --> 30:21.560
-Bravo!
-Truly impressive.

30:30.400 --> 30:33.830
Bravo! Bravo!

30:41.920 --> 30:42.830
Such martial skills.

30:42.830 --> 30:43.640
This is truly impressive!

30:43.640 --> 30:44.480
Really amazing!

30:44.480 --> 30:46.310
His skills are truly impressive.

30:46.310 --> 30:47.310
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

30:49.480 --> 30:50.210
Look at that!

30:52.350 --> 30:52.750
Bravo!

30:57.400 --> 30:58.770
Murder!

31:03.110 --> 31:05.090
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

31:12.960 --> 31:13.820
Your Highness.

31:15.350 --> 31:16.080
How did it go?

31:17.750 --> 31:19.030
There's both good news

31:19.590 --> 31:20.790
and bad news.

31:21.310 --> 31:23.110
Stop keeping us in suspense.
Just tell us the result.

31:23.110 --> 31:23.550
Say it.

31:24.960 --> 31:26.090
The plan succeeded.

31:28.110 --> 31:28.840
However,

31:30.510 --> 31:32.040
all the assassins sent

31:32.550 --> 31:33.720
were wiped out.

31:35.160 --> 31:35.620
Then...

31:36.310 --> 31:36.770
This...

31:38.310 --> 31:39.000
Continue.

31:40.480 --> 31:42.110
As soon as the fight broke out,

31:42.110 --> 31:43.880
the audience scattered in all directions,

31:43.880 --> 31:46.210
and the place descended into total chaos.

31:46.270 --> 31:47.510
That fellow was surrounded

31:47.510 --> 31:49.330
on all sides by the assassins,

31:49.480 --> 31:53.740
yet with a single swift move, he slipped
through a gap in their encirclement,

31:55.830 --> 31:57.560
which was truly unbelievable.

31:57.830 --> 31:59.540
He was clearly stabbed once,

31:59.960 --> 32:02.690
but it didn't seem to affect him
in the slightest.

32:02.790 --> 32:03.960
He kept fighting,

32:05.990 --> 32:07.870
charging left and right.

32:08.200 --> 32:08.790
Then came

32:09.000 --> 32:10.210
a second blow,

32:10.550 --> 32:11.600
and then a third.

32:11.960 --> 32:13.350
Each strike looked fatal,

32:13.350 --> 32:15.610
blades flashing with blood everywhere—

32:17.110 --> 32:21.210
yet he still showed no sign of faltering,
as if nothing were wrong.

32:35.720 --> 32:38.310
Only after he had killed the last assassin

32:38.640 --> 32:41.300
did he let out a long peal of laughter,
"hahaha,"

32:42.550 --> 32:44.150
and then finally collapsed.

32:48.350 --> 32:49.830
Why are you repeating the laughter?

32:49.830 --> 32:52.230
You're here to report,
not to tell stories.

32:52.790 --> 32:53.650
Your Highness.

32:54.720 --> 32:55.920
What I just said

32:56.680 --> 32:58.510
wasn't exaggerated at all.

33:02.240 --> 33:03.840
Where's that expert's body?

33:04.750 --> 33:05.720
After he died,

33:06.110 --> 33:08.640
the officers ordered
the brothel keepers to clean up the scene

33:08.640 --> 33:10.400
and wipe away all the bloodstains.

33:10.400 --> 33:10.720
My Lord.

33:10.720 --> 33:13.400
-I sent someone to buy the body.
-My Lord, the body is here.

33:13.400 --> 33:15.130
And we confirmed his identity.

33:16.440 --> 33:16.970
Who is he?

33:17.720 --> 33:20.560
Based on the body and his belongings,

33:20.750 --> 33:23.680
he was a trusted secret guard
of the Empress Dowager.

33:26.270 --> 33:27.470
The Empress Dowager?

33:28.490 --> 33:30.880
Extremely ruthless
with exceptional skills,

33:30.880 --> 33:32.540
with a long scar on his face.

33:33.270 --> 33:34.070
He was someone

33:34.680 --> 33:38.070
we were specifically
on guard against before.

33:39.200 --> 33:41.600
So you're saying the Empress Dowager's man

33:42.160 --> 33:43.820
was protecting the Emperor?

33:46.880 --> 33:47.340
This...

33:47.480 --> 33:48.920
I never expected

33:48.960 --> 33:51.160
things would turn out like this, either.

33:51.160 --> 33:52.760
Why would the Empress Dowager

33:52.760 --> 33:55.140
suddenly show goodwill to the Emperor?

33:55.310 --> 33:56.860
This is too bizarre.

33:56.920 --> 33:58.440
A-Absolutely impossible.

33:58.440 --> 33:59.440
Have you forgotten

33:59.440 --> 34:01.030
how fiercely they fought

34:01.030 --> 34:03.000
over the Salt-for-Services Policy?

34:03.000 --> 34:04.110
That was an intense confrontation

34:04.110 --> 34:06.000
known to everyone at court.

34:06.160 --> 34:06.960
How could they suddenly...

34:06.960 --> 34:08.000
Or perhaps

34:09.100 --> 34:12.500
he was a spy the Empress Dowager
placed at the Emperor's side.

34:13.699 --> 34:14.159
Then...

34:15.170 --> 34:17.070
Then wouldn't we have killed
the wrong person

34:17.070 --> 34:18.550
and actually helped the Emperor

34:18.550 --> 34:19.679
eliminate a threat?

34:23.510 --> 34:25.969
Gentlemen, there's no need
to overthink it.

34:26.360 --> 34:28.639
Eliminating someone of such special status

34:28.639 --> 34:30.440
actually gives us peace of mind.

34:31.360 --> 34:34.219
At this point, the two of them
are both spent forces.

34:34.800 --> 34:36.730
With the court rife with intrigue,

34:37.590 --> 34:38.449
replacing them

34:39.400 --> 34:40.960
is only a matter of time.

34:42.440 --> 34:43.960
Your Highness is wise.

34:50.120 --> 34:52.000
[Zhang San's Diary]

34:52.070 --> 34:53.360
I heard

34:53.360 --> 34:56.150
you've been coming to the library
every few days.

34:56.710 --> 34:59.190
I thought you were diligently studying.

35:00.000 --> 35:00.860
I didn't expect

35:01.510 --> 35:04.110
you'd be so fond of
these plants and flowers.

35:05.710 --> 35:06.750
Your Majesty,

35:07.280 --> 35:07.910
I

35:08.400 --> 35:10.550
am not wasting time on frivolous pursuits.

35:10.550 --> 35:11.580
I-I'm just...

35:12.590 --> 35:13.150
Just...

35:16.400 --> 35:17.330
Just what?

35:18.190 --> 35:18.630
This...

35:18.630 --> 35:19.430
Your Majesty.

35:19.880 --> 35:20.880
I know I was wrong.

35:21.150 --> 35:22.150
I know I was wrong.

35:24.960 --> 35:26.090
Silly kid.

35:26.760 --> 35:28.290
You've done nothing wrong.

35:30.260 --> 35:32.340
I haven't blamed you for anything.

35:32.590 --> 35:34.390
There's no need to be so nervous.

35:35.670 --> 35:39.190
[SOS]

35:36.190 --> 35:37.510
The late Empress Dowager

35:37.510 --> 35:38.710
once held you

35:39.510 --> 35:40.760
in very high regard.

35:42.070 --> 35:46.110
It's just that she was overly strict
in disciplining you.

35:47.630 --> 35:48.760
I, on the other hand,

35:49.150 --> 35:50.610
have no children of my own.

35:51.630 --> 35:52.260
Why don't

35:53.480 --> 35:54.230
you become

35:54.710 --> 35:56.190
my child instead?

36:00.440 --> 36:02.970
I'm different from
the late Empress Dowager.

36:03.280 --> 36:05.110
I only hope that you, Crown Prince,

36:05.110 --> 36:07.470
can grow up happily.

36:07.760 --> 36:10.280
You don't have to do things
you don't like.

36:10.400 --> 36:11.860
If you don't want to study,

36:11.920 --> 36:12.990
then don't.

36:13.150 --> 36:15.180
If you like these flowers and plants,

36:14.390 --> 36:21.340
[SOS]

36:15.400 --> 36:17.000
then tend to them as you wish.

36:17.510 --> 36:18.320
You see,

36:18.550 --> 36:20.030
his gardening is

36:20.280 --> 36:21.590
actually quite beautiful.

36:21.590 --> 36:22.850
Your Majesty is right.

36:24.510 --> 36:25.400
Your Majesty,

36:26.510 --> 36:27.310
do you mean it?

36:28.710 --> 36:29.810
When I speak,

36:30.190 --> 36:31.520
I always mean what I say.

36:35.440 --> 36:37.280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

36:39.710 --> 36:40.570
Your Highness,

36:40.890 --> 36:42.690
this is an incredible blessing!

36:42.960 --> 36:44.550
Why are you still calling her
"Your Majesty?"

36:44.550 --> 36:46.070
You should change how you address her

36:46.070 --> 36:47.530
and call her "Mother" now.

36:50.320 --> 36:50.920
I

36:51.670 --> 36:53.050
thank you, Mother.

36:58.320 --> 37:00.100
My dear son.

37:00.400 --> 37:01.170
See,

37:01.550 --> 37:02.810
isn't this wonderful?

37:08.150 --> 37:09.410
Look at these flowers.

37:09.480 --> 37:10.710
They're truly exquisite.

37:10.710 --> 37:11.440
Yeah.

37:11.590 --> 37:13.320
And the color is beautiful too.

37:14.590 --> 37:15.990
Let's take a closer look.

37:16.340 --> 37:17.470
Don't go over there.

37:17.550 --> 37:18.480
Let's leave now.

37:19.920 --> 37:20.450
Let's go.

37:21.110 --> 37:21.670
We don't want to be late.

37:21.670 --> 37:22.440
Just one look.

37:22.440 --> 37:24.500
Sister will be worried if we're late.

37:42.440 --> 37:44.300
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

37:51.110 --> 37:52.700
The palace is so vast,

37:53.060 --> 37:54.840
yet His Highness spends every day
just admiring these Hydrangeas

37:54.840 --> 37:56.440
and never seems to tire of it.

37:57.000 --> 37:57.840
Exactly.

37:58.320 --> 37:59.880
You don't think he's possessed by
some flower spirit, do you?
